entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not a lock.\", \"from\": 7157, \"to\": 7175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not that far away, either.\", \"from\": 7176, \"to\": 7213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t lose one 200-meter race over the 2022 and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 seasons.\", \"from\": 7214, \"to\": 7285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before Sunday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s final, Lyles wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t nervous\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094same as Keisha on her walk.\", \"from\": 7287, \"to\": 7364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7312, \"end\": 7317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9890789083176801, \"rank\": 0.011011849229328411, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 7345, \"end\": 7351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He thought back to a regular topic he had been exploring with his therapist.\", \"from\": 7365, \"to\": 7441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To not view pressure as a problem, to understand the notion that wanting something doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t always equate to being able to automatically deliver it.\", \"from\": 7442, \"to\": 7591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was extremely curious to see what was gonna happen,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said.\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI came in third fastest [in the semis.]\", \"from\": 7662, \"to\": 7704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This [was] not going to be easy.\", \"from\": 7705, \"to\": 7737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s how we phrase it.I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m curious what I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m gonna do.How am I going to pull this off?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  His therapist, Lyles said, told him to let go in those moments, to relax and be himself.\", \"from\": 7738, \"to\": 7923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7850, \"end\": 7855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9890789083176801, \"rank\": 0.011011849229328411, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Turns out, to achieve the rarest kind of greatness, and to lift his sport to the same heights he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s headed toward, that was all he ever needed.\", \"from\": 7924, \"to\": 8068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Bishop is a senior writer for Sports Illustrated who has covered every kind of sport and every major event across six continents for more than two decades.\", \"from\": 8070, \"to\": 8230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8070, \"end\": 8081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9999950627965526, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Bishop\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 8105, \"end\": 8123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.225383656757883e-27, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He previously worked for The Seattle Times and The New Y